uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-12-150x100.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-12.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI’m all about a festive dessert and in the past, I’ve shared many christmas cakes. My most popular is \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2017/12/christmas-cake/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ethis white christmas sparkle cake\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e – it is SO good. We also love \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2018/12/pink-peppermint-cake/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ethe pink peppermint cake\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e which looks like it came straight out of the grinch life, my \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2019/12/hot-cocoa-cake/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehot cocoa cake with whipped marshmallow\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e, \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2023/12/white-chocolate-mocha-cake/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ewhite chocolate mocha cake\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e and \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2022/12/spiced-orange-cake/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy spiced orange snowball cake\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOh oh, and who could forget \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2021/12/christmas-ice-cream-cake/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy pink peppermint ice cream cake\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e?! That one really… takes the cake.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSORRY. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-96663\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chocolate peppermint pie\" width=\"1708\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/chocolate-peppermint-pie/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chocolate Fudge Pie with a Peppermint Marshmallow Cloud.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-scaled.jpg 1708w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-728x938.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-768x990.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-1192x1536.jpg 1192w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-1590x2048.jpg 1590w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-150x193.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1708px) 100vw, 1708px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201708%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-scaled.jpg 1708w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-728x938.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-768x990.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-1192x1536.jpg 1192w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-1590x2048.jpg 1590w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-150x193.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-9-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBut P.S.\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4fZEPsD\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e that target peppermint bark ice cream\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e I love this year would go perfectly in that cake!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnyway, this ganache pie is heavenly. It is super rich and chocolatey. The marshmallow meringue on top is so fluffy and light, it really cuts the richness a bit. It also will deflate into the pie after a few hours, but it still tastes fantastic. It just means every bite gets a taste of it. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-14-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chocolate peppermint pie\" width=\"1685\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/chocolate-peppermint-pie/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chocolate Fudge Pie with a Peppermint Marshmallow Cloud.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-14-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-14-scaled.jpg 1685w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-14-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-14-768x1003.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-14-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-14-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-