/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003ePink Peppermint Chocolate Fudge Pie\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"96679\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003cspan\u003e hour\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChill Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003cspan\u003e hours\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003cspan\u003e hours\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis chocolate peppermint pie is an indulgent pretty dessert for the holiday season! A crunchy oreo crust, a fudgy chocolate ganache filling all topped with a peppermint marshmallow meringue cloud - it\u0026#39;s dreamy!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"96679\" data-servings=\"8\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(13 ounce)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e package oreo cookies\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/salted-butter-1lb-good-gather-8482/-/A-54445965?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebutter,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003emelted\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003edark chocolate,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/heavy-whipping-cream-16-fl-oz-1pt-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54550905?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eheavy cream\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/land-o-lakes-unsalted-butter-1lb/-/A-13227053?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eunsalted butter,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eat room temperature, cut into pieces\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/vital-farms-pasture-raised-grade-a-large-eggs-12ct/-/A-18783617?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003elarge egg whites\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/granulated-sugar-4lbs-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-78471310?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ewhite sugar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/cream-of-tartar-3-25oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-85386978?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ecream of tartar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/mccormick-pure-vanilla-extract-1oz/-/A-13353205?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003evanilla extract\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epeppermint extract\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003edrop of red food coloring,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eif you wish\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"96679\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the oreos in the bowl of a food processor and pulse until crumbs remain.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a large bowl, combine the oreo crumbs and melted butter. Stir until combined and the crumbs are all moistened. Press the mixture in a 9-inch pie plate to form a crust. Stick the crust in the fridge while you make the filling.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the chocolate in a large bowl. Heat the heavy cream in a saucepan over medium-low heat, until just hot, but not bubbling. Pour the cream over the chopped chocolate. Let sit for 1 to 2 minutes without stirring. After 2 minutes, stir continuously until a ganache comes together and the chocolate is smooth. Stir in the butter until completely melted.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePour the chocolate ganache into the pie crust, smoothing out the top. Place the pie dish back in the fridge for at least 2 hours or even overnight.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo make the marshmallow topping, combine the egg whites, sugar and cream of tartar in a heat-proof bowl, preferably the bowl of your electric stand mixer. Place over top of a double-boiler that contains simmering water, and whisk constantly for 3 to 4 minutes until the sugar has dissolved and the egg whites are slightly warm. Immediately remove the bowl and place it on your stand mixer with the whisk attachment, beating slowly at first and gradually increasing the speed to high.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBeat for 6 to 7 minutes until glossy and thick, then beat in the vanilla and peppermint extract for another minute until combined. This is where you can swirl in a drop of red food coloring if you\u0026#39;d like! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-6\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePile the frosting on top of the ganache right before serving. You can do this about 1 hour ahead of time if needed. Slice and serve! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-96679-step-0-7\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis stays great in the fridge if you make it ahead of time - just wait to top with the marshmallow until close to serving time. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDessert\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chocolate peppermint pie\" width=\"1720\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/12/chocolate-peppermint-pie/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chocolate Fudge Pie with a Peppermint Marshmallow Cloud.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-scaled.jpg 1720w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-728x931.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-768x982.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-1201x1536.jpg 1201w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-1601x2048.jpg 1601w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1720px) 100vw, 1720px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201720%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-scaled.jpg 1720w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-728x931.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-768x982.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-1201x1536.jpg 1201w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-1601x2048.jpg 1601w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-150x192.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/pink-peppermint-chocolate-cream-pie-15-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u0